		<p>This Bible Access List is a research initiative identifying where it is most difficult for people to access Bibles and highlights the nations with the most significant shortages. The results are based on expert analysis of 34 data points and insights from consultations with over a thousand national experts.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="bg-white dark:bg-stone-900 py-24 sm:py-32">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
		  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 items-center gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:grid-cols-2">
			<div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-xl lg:mx-0">
			  <img class="max-h-16 w-full object-contain object-left" src="https://bibleaccesslist.org/images/logo/bai_logo_title.svg" alt="Bible Access Initative" />
			  <p class="mt-6 text-lg/8 text-stone-600">Advancing the Worldwide Distribution and Multiplication of Bible Resources through strategic research, collaboration, and a shared passion for Godâ€™s Word. The Bible Access Initiative is a growing collobrative of ministry partners committed to focusing efforts toward insuring God's Word is globally accessible and available.</p>
			  <div class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-x-6">
				<a href="#" class="rounded-md bg-orange-700 px-3.5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-xs hover:bg-orange-800 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-600">Join Us!</a>
				<a href="#" class="text-sm font-semibold text-stone-900">Contact Us <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a>
			  </div>
			</div>
			<div class="mx-auto grid w-full max-w-xl grid-cols-2 items-center gap-x-4 gap-y-6 md:gap-y-8 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:pl-8">
			  <a href="https://www.bibleleague.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" title="Bible League International"><img class="max-h-16 w-full object-contain object-center" src="https://bibleaccesslist.org/images/logo/bli.svg" alt="Bible League International" width="130" /></a>
			  <a href="https://www.dbs.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" title="Digital Bible Society"><img class="max-h-12 w-full object-contain object-center" src="https://bibleaccesslist.org/images/logo/dbs_banner.svg" alt="Digital Bible Society" width="104" height="48" /></a>
			  <a href="https://closethebiblegap.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" title="Bible League International"><img class="max-h-16 w-full object-contain object-center" src="https://bibleaccesslist.org/images/logo/ctbg.svg" alt="Close the Bible Gap" width="140" height="48" /></a>
			  <a href="https://frontlinesinternational.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" title="Frontlines International"><img class="max-h-16 w-full object-contain object-center" src="https://bibleaccesslist.org/images/logo/frontlines.svg" alt="Frontlines International" width="136" height="48" /></a>
			  <a href="https://www.opendoors.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" title="Bible League International"><img class="max-h-10 w-full object-contain object-center" src="https://bibleaccesslist.org/images/logo/odi.svg" alt="Open Doors" width="136" height="48" /></a>
			</div>
		  </div>
		</div>
	  </div>
</Layout>
